Summary: Black object resembling a bat or insect zipping and zig-zagging from cloud to camera and back
divs: Sighting DetailsI was video-taping at random and caught this object. It appears to become visible just beyond a large cloud. It comes through and around the cloud, then comes toward the camera. It goes out of camera range and comes back, then goes back to the cloud. All this happens in less than 2 seconds. Video attached.
